SQL> SELECT e.ename, d.loc
  2  FROM emp e
  3  JOIN dept d ON e.deptno = d.deptno
  4  WHERE d.loc = 'CHICAGO';

ENAME      LOC
---------- -------------
ALLEN      CHICAGO
WARD       CHICAGO
MARTIN     CHICAGO
BLAKE      CHICAGO
TURNER     CHICAGO
JAMES      CHICAGO

